Spark Kosam: Data Integrity Checking
-- Find employees assigned to projects that are ON_HOLD
SELECT name
FROM employees
WHERE emp_id IN (
    SELECT ep.emp_id
    FROM employee_projects ep
    JOIN projects p ON ep.project_id = p.project_id
    WHERE p.status = 'ON_HOLD'
);
Enduku: Delivery risk report, Resource reallocation

-- EXISTS vs IN (Idi Performance chespthundii)
SELECT e.name
FROM employees e
WHERE EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM employee_projects ep
    JOIN projects p ON ep.project_id = p.project_id
    WHERE ep.emp_id = e.emp_id
      AND p.status = 'ON_HOLD'
);

EXISTS -> when checking existence
IN -> when subquery result is small
JOIN -> when fetching related data
NOT EXISTS -> instead of NOT IN

-- Anti-Join Pattern (Bench people kosam)
Find employees not assigned to any project
SELECT name
FROM employees e
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM employee_projects ep
    WHERE ep.emp_id = e.emp_id
);
Endukantee: Utilization reports, Bench tracking, SLA compliance

